  "description": "<p>日媒12日报道，<strong>日本科技公司Century近日推出了一款女性用照明雨伞“bright night”，售价3980日元（约人民币240元）。</strong>该雨伞的内侧顶端设计有一颗照明电灯，可以为伞下直径180cm的范围提供照明，开发公司表示，该 照明雨伞能够为雨天夜间道路行走的女性提供更加安全的保障。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e8f9b9d/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244472.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E7%94%A8%E7%94%B5%E7%81%AF%E9%9B%A8%E4%BC%9E\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244472.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E7%94%A8%E7%94%B5%E7%81%AF%E9%9B%A8%E4%BC%9E\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244472.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E7%94%A8%E7%94%B5%E7%81%AF%E9%9B%A8%E4%BC%9E\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244472.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E7%94%A8%E7%94%B5%E7%81%AF%E9%9B%A8%E4%BC%9E\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244472.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E7%94%A8%E7%94%B5%E7%81%AF%E9%9B%A8%E4%BC%9E\" target=\"_b